<h1>Cheonjiyeon Falls</h1>
<p>We started the day by taking a scenic drive to Cheonjiyeon Falls (easily confused with Cheonjeyeon Falls because the names are spelled almost exactly the same). Very popular with lots of tourist buses, it is located in the southwest corner of Seogwipo. It's a short walk to the waterfall, and you will have to wait in line to take photos in front of the waterfall. For my kids, the main attraction were the ducks and fish.</p>

