<h1>Seogwipo Maeil Olle Market</h1>
<p>For our next stop and lunch, we went to a street market that is packed with what you would expect, but I did notice an oversupply (yet high prices) of oranges, apple-mangoes, and fresh-squeezed juice (which is quite delicious on a hot summer day). The fried black-pig-pork is very popular and very delicious. And the lady draws a happy pig face with the bbq sauce.</p>
